  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT277-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ pirintavaḻi avaṉ kuṟitta paruva varavu tōḻi aṟivāraik kaṇṭu
          viṉāyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Asked by the confidante when seeing some savants,
          [concerning] the coming of the season he had intended [for his return] when HE separated. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT277">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> āci ṟeruvi ṉāyil viyaṉkaṭaic</l>
          <l> cenne lamalai veṇmai veḷḷiḻu</l>
          <l> tōriṟ piccai yāra mānti</l>
          <l> yaṟcira veyya veppat taṇṇīrc</l>
          <l> cēmac ceppiṟ peṟīiyarō nīyē</l>
          <l> miṉṉiṭai naṭuṅkuṅ kaṭaippeyal vāṭai</l>
          <l> yekkāl varuva teṉṟi</l>
          <l> yakkāl varuvareṅ kāta lōrē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>You, may you obtain in a safe vessel</l>
          <l rend="indent2">of hot fresh water, hot [draughts] in the cold season</l>
          <l>[and] eat [your] fill with the alms of a single house,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">very white ghee with boiled red rice</l>
          <l rend="indent5">at a wide gate without dogs in a flawless street! </l>
          <l>When would you say it will come,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">the north wind with the last raining,</l>
          <l rend="indent8">when [one] shivers in midst of lightning? </l>
          <l>At that time he will come, our lover.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
